fields.history_note: The whole is hand made by various members of one family and used for many years.  There are present season notebooks and reference books to the teams and their performances

Rules:
The game is a cross between a race and a strategy game with the winner being the `team' with the greatest number of points.  Plays are determined by cards

Rules placement: separate book
